      "widgets_values": [
        "### First-time ID flow only\n1. Leave `existing_group_id` empty\n2. Queue `SeedanceCreateHumanAsset`\n3. Click **Start Verification** inside the node\n4. Complete the H5 liveness check\n5. Queue `SeedanceCreateHumanAsset` again\n6. Save both `group_id` and `asset_id`\n\n### After that\nUse the returned `asset_id` in a separate generation workflow by connecting it to `Seedance2.human_asset_id`.\n\nThis avoids running the video generation node before the verified `asset_id` exists."
      ]
